1
00:00:07,060 --> 00:00:09,060
It's been several days
since Xieyun escaped

2
00:00:09,060 --> 00:00:10,260
from the Fushi Mirror.

3
00:00:10,900 --> 00:00:11,940
Any progress?

4
00:00:14,460 --> 00:00:15,260
Master,

5
00:00:15,980 --> 00:00:16,860
Xieyun

6
00:00:17,500 --> 00:00:18,460
has entered

7
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:19,940
a mortal's body

8
00:00:21,500 --> 00:00:22,220
and is now

9
00:00:22,420 --> 00:00:23,620
under Xiyin's care.

10
00:00:24,460 --> 00:00:25,900
She likely intends to save that mortal.

11
00:00:27,460 --> 00:00:28,260
I think

12
00:00:29,060 --> 00:00:30,660
if he stops doing evil,

13
00:00:31,340 --> 00:00:31,740
perhaps we could...

14
00:00:43,260 --> 00:00:44,460
If Xieyun grows stronger,

15
00:00:45,300 --> 00:00:47,340
it will bring catastrophe
to the Three Realms.

16
00:00:48,220 --> 00:00:49,420
No matter what,

17
00:00:50,300 --> 00:00:51,660
it must be eliminated.

18
00:00:53,740 --> 00:00:54,820
Understood.

19
00:00:55,560 --> 00:00:57,800
[Immortal Beyond Dust]
[Episode 10]

20
00:01:02,860 --> 00:01:03,380
Let me go!

21
00:01:03,900 --> 00:01:04,860
I haven't done anything wrong.

22
00:01:05,900 --> 00:01:06,420
Let go of me!

23
00:01:07,140 --> 00:01:07,940
Immortal Venerable,

24
00:01:08,620 --> 00:01:10,340
Yaoyang injured three of my disciples

25
00:01:10,540 --> 00:01:11,780
and nearly took their lives.

26
00:01:12,460 --> 00:01:14,260
If Xieyun inside him
isn't sealed away soon,

27
00:01:14,460 --> 00:01:15,500
it will cause great chaos.

28
00:01:16,220 --> 00:01:18,260
Immortal Venerable,
please make your decision.

29
00:01:18,780 --> 00:01:20,740
Dehua, you're absolutely right.

30
00:01:21,140 --> 00:01:22,300
By law,

31
00:01:22,780 --> 00:01:24,220
Yaoyang's crime doesn't warrant death.

32
00:01:25,300 --> 00:01:27,740
He will receive
twenty-four heavenly thunder strikes

33
00:01:27,900 --> 00:01:30,380
and be imprisoned forever
in the Nether Tower.

34
00:01:31,180 --> 00:01:32,340
Immortal Venerable,
your judgment is wise.

35
00:01:34,260 --> 00:01:34,780
Immortal Venerable,

36
00:01:35,380 --> 00:01:36,380
Yaoyang's mistake

37
00:01:36,740 --> 00:01:38,460
is due to my failure
to keep watch over him.

38
00:01:39,100 --> 00:01:40,340
Please punish me.

39
00:01:41,980 --> 00:01:42,940
Immortal Xiyin,

40
00:01:43,460 --> 00:01:44,780
a fiend is still a fiend.

41
00:01:45,220 --> 00:01:46,700
You've ignored the disciples of the sect

42
00:01:46,700 --> 00:01:48,020
and only protected this fiend.

43
00:01:48,860 --> 00:01:50,260
What are your intentions?

44
00:01:52,020 --> 00:01:52,860
Immortal Venerable, please calm down.

45
00:01:54,420 --> 00:01:55,020
Yaoyang

46
00:01:55,780 --> 00:01:57,140
is my disciple.

47
00:01:57,620 --> 00:01:58,660
When a disciple makes a mistake,

48
00:01:58,980 --> 00:02:01,380
it's only right that the master
bears the punishment.

49
00:02:01,940 --> 00:02:02,740
Besides,

50
00:02:03,540 --> 00:02:04,260
Yaoyang

51
00:02:04,780 --> 00:02:06,140
isn't a born a fiend.

52
00:02:06,740 --> 00:02:08,260
It was Xieyun inside him that caused him

53
00:02:08,260 --> 00:02:09,540
to harm his fellow disciples.

54
00:02:09,780 --> 00:02:11,260
There's more to this situation.

55
00:02:11,740 --> 00:02:13,580
Immortal Venerable,
please see the truth.

56
00:02:15,420 --> 00:02:16,700
Xiyin, are you ignoring

57
00:02:16,700 --> 00:02:18,020
the rules of the immortal sect?

58
00:02:18,460 --> 00:02:19,580
Today,

59
00:02:19,980 --> 00:02:21,140
those three disciples

60
00:02:21,420 --> 00:02:23,100
tried to eliminate
a pure-natured fox demon,

61
00:02:23,100 --> 00:02:24,460
mistaking it for an evil one.

62
00:02:24,460 --> 00:02:25,220
My disciple

63
00:02:25,780 --> 00:02:27,980
only stepped in to uphold justice.

64
00:02:28,940 --> 00:02:32,220
Xieyun is formed from evil thoughts.

65
00:02:32,980 --> 00:02:35,460
How can someone filled with malice

66
00:02:35,820 --> 00:02:37,620
harbor any good?

67
00:02:38,180 --> 00:02:39,220
All things have two sides.

68
00:02:39,660 --> 00:02:40,740
Good and evil oppose each other.

69
00:02:41,020 --> 00:02:43,940
Since there is no absolute good
in this world,

70
00:02:44,380 --> 00:02:46,540
there can be no absolute evil either.

71
00:02:47,420 --> 00:02:48,140
Besides,

72
00:02:48,580 --> 00:02:49,940
Yaoyang has no cultivation yet.

73
00:02:50,380 --> 00:02:52,260
How could he withstand
twenty-four heavenly thunder strikes?

74
00:02:56,380 --> 00:02:58,940
The Nether Tower
is filled with wicked demons.

75
00:02:59,540 --> 00:03:01,220
If Xieyun absorbs their power

76
00:03:01,220 --> 00:03:02,380
and breaks free,

77
00:03:02,380 --> 00:03:03,580
it would be disastrous.

78
00:03:05,420 --> 00:03:07,660
Immortal Venerable, please reconsider.

79
00:03:08,380 --> 00:03:10,060
But our disciples

80
00:03:10,060 --> 00:03:11,660
can't be injured for nothing.

81
00:03:12,380 --> 00:03:14,980
This matter must be settled.

82
00:03:18,540 --> 00:03:19,340
I

83
00:03:19,780 --> 00:03:21,020
will accept the punishment
in my disciple's place.

84
00:03:21,220 --> 00:03:21,700
Alright.

85
00:03:21,700 --> 00:03:22,660
No, Master.

86
00:03:22,660 --> 00:03:23,460
Heng.

87
00:03:24,620 --> 00:03:27,220
You will oversee the punishment.

88
00:03:28,540 --> 00:03:28,980
Yes.

89
00:03:37,540 --> 00:03:38,060
Heng,

90
00:03:38,740 --> 00:03:39,980
take Yang back.

91
00:03:40,100 --> 00:03:40,740
I'm not leaving.

92
00:03:41,460 --> 00:03:41,980
Master,

93
00:03:42,420 --> 00:03:44,020
I want to stay with you!

94
00:03:44,180 --> 00:03:45,300
Just a few thunder strikes.

95
00:03:45,820 --> 00:03:46,420
I'll be fine.

96
00:03:47,060 --> 00:03:47,620
I won't leave.

97
00:03:47,940 --> 00:03:48,420
Go!

98
00:03:48,420 --> 00:03:48,900
I won't go!

99
00:03:49,540 --> 00:03:49,860
Go!

100
00:03:49,860 --> 00:03:50,460
I'm not leaving.

101
00:03:51,220 --> 00:03:51,780
Go now!

102
00:03:51,780 --> 00:03:52,220
I won't.

103
00:03:52,220 --> 00:03:52,620
Go!

104
00:03:52,740 --> 00:03:53,340
Master.

105
00:03:53,900 --> 00:03:54,620
Master!

106
00:03:55,100 --> 00:03:55,700
Yaoyang,

107
00:03:56,340 --> 00:03:58,100
in the end, it was my fault
that you became a fiend.

108
00:03:58,420 --> 00:03:59,020
Today,

109
00:03:59,380 --> 00:04:00,500
I'll repay your life

110
00:04:00,660 --> 00:04:01,500
with mine.

111
00:04:17,100 --> 00:04:18,340
Was she just lying to me?

112
00:04:19,060 --> 00:04:20,780
What will happen to her if she takes

113
00:04:22,180 --> 00:04:22,940
twenty-four heavenly thunder strikes?

114
00:04:29,700 --> 00:04:30,300
In the past,

115
00:04:30,820 --> 00:04:31,940
an immortal

116
00:04:31,940 --> 00:04:33,380
took only fifteen heavenly thunder strikes

117
00:04:33,380 --> 00:04:34,860
and his soul was injured.

118
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:36,580
He still hasn't recovered.

119
00:04:38,060 --> 00:04:38,820
And now

120
00:04:39,740 --> 00:04:41,500
Xiyin is going to take

121
00:04:41,500 --> 00:04:42,980
twenty-four strikes for you.

122
00:04:44,780 --> 00:04:45,580
My master...

123
00:04:46,900 --> 00:04:48,100
She...

124
00:04:48,100 --> 00:04:48,740
No.

125
00:04:53,460 --> 00:04:54,260
Stop this!

126
00:04:55,340 --> 00:04:56,380
Don't!

127
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:06,200
♪If immortals can't linger for love♪

128
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:13,040
♪If mortals can't bind fate
for affection♪

129
00:05:13,520 --> 00:05:15,460
♪Oh gods, please♪

130
00:05:15,460 --> 00:05:16,060
Master!

131
00:05:16,940 --> 00:05:18,580
Let me in, Master!

132
00:05:19,500 --> 00:05:20,180
Leave!

133
00:05:21,540 --> 00:05:22,260
Go now.

134
00:05:23,860 --> 00:05:24,860
I won't go.

135
00:05:25,460 --> 00:05:26,460
I won't!

136
00:05:26,460 --> 00:05:29,760
♪Even if we must wait
another thousand years♪

137
00:05:40,080 --> 00:05:46,480
♪I watch you descend
to the mortal world♪

138
00:05:49,500 --> 00:05:50,380
I'm sorry.

139
00:05:50,380 --> 00:05:54,880
♪Slowly I let go of the thread I hold♪

140
00:05:55,680 --> 00:06:01,760
♪If immortals can't linger for love♪

141
00:06:02,080 --> 00:06:08,540
♪If mortals can't bind fate
for affection♪

142
00:06:08,540 --> 00:06:09,340
Master,

143
00:06:10,100 --> 00:06:11,020
are you alright?

144
00:06:11,900 --> 00:06:12,900
Don't worry.

145
00:06:13,820 --> 00:06:14,820
I'm fine.

146
00:06:15,660 --> 00:06:16,860
Master,

147
00:06:17,380 --> 00:06:18,420
I'm sorry.

148
00:06:19,180 --> 00:06:20,220
This is all my fault.

149
00:06:20,740 --> 00:06:21,940
I'm the one who got you into this.

150
00:06:23,020 --> 00:06:24,220
I'm alright.

151
00:06:27,820 --> 00:06:28,620
Step aside!

152
00:06:46,540 --> 00:06:47,740
How is my master?

153
00:06:49,340 --> 00:06:49,900
Xiyin,

154
00:06:51,100 --> 00:06:52,660
why put yourself through this?

155
00:06:55,700 --> 00:06:56,500
Enough,

156
00:06:57,140 --> 00:06:57,940
Heng.

157
00:07:02,060 --> 00:07:03,100
From now on,

158
00:07:04,380 --> 00:07:06,140
you must train diligently
in immortal arts.

159
00:07:06,940 --> 00:07:08,420
Don't let all your master's effort

160
00:07:08,620 --> 00:07:10,260
go to waste.

161
00:07:11,300 --> 00:07:11,900
Alright.

162
00:07:12,500 --> 00:07:13,100
Heng.

163
00:07:14,460 --> 00:07:15,540
I'm fine now.

164
00:07:20,780 --> 00:07:21,420
Yang,

165
00:07:23,340 --> 00:07:23,900
let's

166
00:07:24,980 --> 00:07:25,700
go home.

167
00:07:38,450 --> 00:07:39,300
[Fuxian Morning Dew]

168
00:07:39,300 --> 00:07:40,260
Fuxian Morning Dew

169
00:07:40,900 --> 00:07:42,020
has healing properties.

170
00:07:47,460 --> 00:07:48,260
Master.

171
00:07:48,700 --> 00:07:49,500
Wait here.

172
00:07:50,300 --> 00:07:51,700
I'll go collect the morning dew now.

173
00:08:29,100 --> 00:08:29,540
Who's there?

174
00:08:30,140 --> 00:08:30,660
Show yourself!

175
00:08:31,620 --> 00:08:32,020
It's me.

176
00:08:32,940 --> 00:08:34,420
You're that fox demon from before?

177
00:08:35,700 --> 00:08:37,820
Thanks to you and that immortal,

178
00:08:38,060 --> 00:08:39,100
I escaped disaster.

179
00:08:40,460 --> 00:08:41,860
Are you collecting

180
00:08:42,900 --> 00:08:44,020
morning dew?

181
00:08:45,980 --> 00:08:47,500
My master was injured because of me.

182
00:08:48,180 --> 00:08:49,300
I heard the dew here

183
00:08:49,900 --> 00:08:51,060
helps restore immortal the body.

184
00:08:51,420 --> 00:08:52,460
Let me help you.

185
00:09:10,860 --> 00:09:11,900
Fuxianl Morning Dew?

186
00:09:14,860 --> 00:09:15,420
Master,

187
00:09:15,940 --> 00:09:17,060
are you feeling better?

188
00:09:17,900 --> 00:09:19,420
That fox demon I saved

189
00:09:19,900 --> 00:09:20,700
helped me get this.

190
00:09:21,300 --> 00:09:22,620
Repaying kindness.

191
00:09:23,260 --> 00:09:24,420
Not all demons are evil.

192
00:09:25,900 --> 00:09:26,380
Yang,

193
00:09:26,980 --> 00:09:28,380
you went through such effort

194
00:09:28,380 --> 00:09:29,980
to collect the morning dew for me.

195
00:09:30,460 --> 00:09:31,820
I'm really glad.

196
00:09:33,100 --> 00:09:34,660
Master, you were injured because of me.

197
00:09:35,420 --> 00:09:36,100
Of course

198
00:09:36,620 --> 00:09:38,060
I'd try to heal you.

199
00:09:39,220 --> 00:09:40,180
But...

200
00:09:41,020 --> 00:09:41,820
Master,

201
00:09:43,020 --> 00:09:44,420
you didn't have to
take the punishment for me.

202
00:09:45,300 --> 00:09:46,020
That was my respon...

203
00:09:46,020 --> 00:09:47,100
What foolish talk is that?

204
00:09:47,540 --> 00:09:49,020
As your master,

205
00:09:49,420 --> 00:09:50,660
it's my duty to protect you.

206
00:09:51,460 --> 00:09:52,420
I'm mostly fine now.

207
00:09:52,820 --> 00:09:53,980
Don't blame yourself.

208
00:09:56,300 --> 00:09:57,660
Master, you're so good to me.

209
00:09:58,180 --> 00:09:59,580
How can I ever repay you?

210
00:09:59,820 --> 00:10:01,020
If you really want to repay me,

211
00:10:01,260 --> 00:10:03,020
then train hard with me,

212
00:10:03,300 --> 00:10:04,420
get rid of Xieyun,

213
00:10:04,820 --> 00:10:05,900
and get back to normal.

214
00:10:06,220 --> 00:10:07,020
That's it?

215
00:10:07,660 --> 00:10:09,540
Just cultivating with you?

216
00:10:13,900 --> 00:10:14,860
In the mortal realm, they say

217
00:10:15,420 --> 00:10:16,100
no one

218
00:10:16,340 --> 00:10:18,100
helps another without reason

219
00:10:18,420 --> 00:10:19,020
unless

220
00:10:19,300 --> 00:10:20,220
they have an ulterior motive.

221
00:10:20,900 --> 00:10:21,980
Master, why are you

222
00:10:23,020 --> 00:10:24,020
doing all this?

223
00:10:52,140 --> 00:10:54,880
♪What is flickering?♪

224
00:10:55,100 --> 00:10:57,620
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

225
00:10:57,780 --> 00:11:03,620
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

226
00:11:03,660 --> 00:11:06,500
♪What is falling?♪

227
00:11:06,940 --> 00:11:09,740
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

228
00:11:09,980 --> 00:11:15,180
♪Like enduring too many farewells♪

229
00:11:16,100 --> 00:11:17,700
♪When petals drift down♪

230
00:11:17,740 --> 00:11:19,200
♪When the rain falls all around♪

231
00:11:19,300 --> 00:11:21,900
♪I gaze into your eyes♪

232
00:11:22,060 --> 00:11:23,760
♪Beyond the dunes♪

233
00:11:23,860 --> 00:11:25,140
♪No end in sight♪

234
00:11:25,140 --> 00:11:28,140
♪I am like a mayfly♪

235
00:11:28,300 --> 00:11:29,700
♪I won't ask what the future holds♪

236
00:11:29,740 --> 00:11:31,200
♪Nor will I run away♪

237
00:11:31,220 --> 00:11:34,160
♪Through all seasons by my side♪

238
00:11:34,160 --> 00:11:39,420
♪Searching for sparks in the dust♪

239
00:11:53,740 --> 00:11:56,480
♪What is flickering?♪

240
00:11:56,700 --> 00:11:59,180
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

241
00:11:59,380 --> 00:12:05,180
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

242
00:12:05,620 --> 00:12:08,420
♪What is falling?♪

243
00:12:08,540 --> 00:12:11,360
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

244
00:12:11,580 --> 00:12:16,580
♪Like enduring too many farewells♪

245
00:12:17,700 --> 00:12:19,180
♪When petals drift down♪

246
00:12:19,180 --> 00:12:20,680
♪When the rain falls all around♪

247
00:12:20,780 --> 00:12:23,340
♪I gaze into your eyes♪
